HEADWORD: Postiler
<hw>Pos"til*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Written also
<ets>postiller</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who writers marginal notes; one
who illustrates the text of a book by notes in the margin.</def>
<rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

